@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cwhhsy(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.abs((v2 - wp.abs(v2 + 0.19)))
    v0 = v2
    v0 = ((0.59 - wp.cos(v2 + 0.76)) * wp.abs((v1 + 0.96 + tmp + 0.09)))
    data[tid] = v0
